:{"origin":26860,"position":0},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debate: Best answer to a fool is silence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Imam al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah be pleased with him, said in his poetry, \u201cIf a fool speaks to you, do not answer him, for the best answer is silence. If you speak to him, you have delighted him. If you leave him, he nearly dies in anguish.\u201d Source: Di\u0304wa\u0304n al-Ima\u0304m al-Sha\u0304fi\u2019i\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34348,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/08\/04\/shafii-on-too-much-debate\/","url_meta":{"origin":26860,"position":1},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debate: Too much debating belittles status of knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 4, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn \u2018Abd al-Hakam reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAmong the degradation of knowledge is that you debate everyone who debates you, or you argue with everyone who argues with you.\u201d And he said, \u201cKnowledge is ignorance to the people of ignorance, just as ignorance is ignorance\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21512,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/07\/shafii-fiqh-imam-deen\/","url_meta":{"origin":26860,"position":2},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Fiqh: You must understand religion